      "content": "I hear you, and it's okay to feel that way. Sometimes, letting go can be a way to find peace. But remember, it's not about pretending or fighting anymore. It's about finding a way to live with what you have, even if it's not what you wanted. You don't have to fight anymore, but you don't have to give up either. It's okay to just be, and it's okay to not be okay. Just remember, even in silence, you're still here. And that's something worth holding onto.",
